BMC api auto test framework

1.Place file bmc_api_unittest.zip on /home/admin
2.run command : sudo su 
3.run command : unzip bmc_api_unittest.zip 
4.run command : cd bmc_api_unittest 
5.run command : ./install.sh 
6.Copy bios,bmc and fpga images to this following path 

        BMC_IMAGE_PATH = '/home/admin/img/flash-as58xx-cl'
        BIOS_IMAGE_PATH = '/home/admin/img/bios.bin'
        FPGA_IMAGE_PATH = '/home/admin/img/fpga.bin'

7. Copy cpld images to this following path 

        - fishbone48

        FAN_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_1_cpu_pwr.vme'
        BASE_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_2_cpu_pwr.vme'
        CPU_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_3_cpu_pwr.vme'
        SW_CPLD1 = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_4_cpu_pwr.vme'
        SW_CPLD2 = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_5_cpu_pwr.vme'
        FAN_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_1_transfr_bmc.vme'
        BASE_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as13-32h_cpld_2_transfr_bmc.vme'

        - fishbone48

        FAN_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_1_cpu_pwr.vme'
        BASE_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_2_cpu_pwr.vme'
        CPU_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_3_cpu_pwr.vme'
        SW_CPLD1 = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_4_cpu_pwr.vme'
        SW_CPLD2 = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_5_cpu_pwr.vme'
        FAN_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_1_transfr_bmc.vme'
        BASE_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as13-48f8h_cpld_2_transfr_bmc.vme'

        - phalanx

        FAN_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_1_main_cpu_pwr.vme'
        BASE_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_2_main_cpu_pwr.vme'
        CPU_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_3_main_cpu_pwr.vme'
        TOP_LC_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_1_sub_cpu_pwr.vme'
        BOT_LC_CPLD = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_2_sub_cpu_pwr.vme'
        FAN_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_1_transfr_bmc.vme'
        BASE_CPLD_REFRESH = '/home/admin/img/as23-128h_cpld_2_transfr_bmc.vme'


7.run command : cd /home/admin/api_unittest
8.run the test command:

        - to run auto test without test cases that will cause CPU reboot
                ./api_unittest

        - to run manual test with test cases that will cause CPU reboot

                1. Modify SKIP_REBOOT_CPU variable on unittest_config.py to False

                2. Run following command

                Note.For each step cpu will be reboot
        
                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL  
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_bmcutil.TestBMCUtil.test_power_cycle_cpu   

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL                                   
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_bmcutil.TestBMCUtil.test_power_cycle_system

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL  
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_fpga

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL    
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_bios

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL     
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_cpu_cpld   

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL    
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_fan_cpld     

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL                                  
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_base_cpld  
                      
                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL  
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_cpld1  

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL        
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_cpld2     

                export BMC_TEST_PLATFORM=CEL  
                ./api_unittest --run-tests test_fwmgrutil_refresh.TestFirmwareRefreshUtil.test_firmware_refresh_cpld

